<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.1.5">
<l>avaravar tamatama taṟivaṟi vakaivakai</l>
<l>yavarava riṟaiyava reṉavaṭi yaṭaivarka</l>
<l>ḷavarava riṟaiyavar kuṟaivila riṟaiyava</l>
<l>ravaravar vitivaḻi yaṭaiyaniṉ ṟaṉarē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who approach [his] feet, each saying “he is the lord”</l>
<l>in any manner known to each of them,</l>
<l>being lords over them all, being without want</l>
<l>they all are established close to the ordained way of the lord.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
